    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE</strong>: This game is for <strong>Live Streams ONLY.</strong> Currently supports <strong>Twitch</strong> and <strong>Kick</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coin Slots Live is an interactive slots game designed specifically for live streamers. Run the game on stream, connect your <strong>Twitch</strong> or Kick channel, and let your chat participate in real time by spinning slots, earning currency, and triggering shared outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is built to be easy to set up and stream-friendly, making it ideal for both active gameplay and background interaction. Viewers stay engaged while streamers retain control over pacing, sessions, and how chat interacts with the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coin Slots Live is focused on creating entertaining, community driven moments on stream, with ongoing development aimed at expanding features, customization, and progression. <strong>No</strong> real world gambling is involved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200800/extras/019ff6936d30e4c42de6d0baca356f1f.poster.avif?t=1771952266\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200800/extras/019ff6936d30e4c42de6d0baca356f1f.webm?t=1771952266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200800/extras/019ff6936d30e4c42de6d0baca356f1f.mp4?t=1771952266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are currently in Early Access, developing the game's outcome alongside the community and streamers. All feedback and suggestions are welcome during the development process!</p>",
